Much of the interface is provided for completeness and for use
internally by find\-modules loaded by Module mode.  Most user code
should simply call:
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
find_package(<package> [major[.minor]] [EXACT] [REQUIRED|QUIET])
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
