skipped if \fBNO_SYSTEM_ENVIRONMENT_PATH\fP is passed.  Path entries
ending in \fB/bin\fP or \fB/sbin\fP are automatically converted to their
parent directories:
.INDENT 3.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
PATH
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
.IP 5. 3
